{"tid":2068870,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PS4]GUNDAM BATTLE OPERATION 2[84] 1001放咗2日都無人","createTime":"2020-06-18T04:03:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T10:30:27.000Z","uid":7232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"bda624cc6c1468a332e510ed11fa4672e7dc02f6","tid":2068870,"uid":7232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:03:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.atwikiimg.com/www65.atwiki.jp/battle-operation2/attach/635/3236/200611_a9oBkeoq3_jp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.atwikiimg.com%2Fwww65.atwiki.jp%2Fbattle-operation2%2Fattach%2F635%2F3236%2F200611_a9oBkeoq3_jp.png&h=210948d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由於近期軍團戰人數不足<br />\n為方便各位巴打參戰，依家會跟據軍團戰參加意向分軍團<br />\n而新入團都請填表<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1ivpW-JmDfQvJexG0DVCQ-HWCVEaSoFL1cSjw1Ns_Qmw/edit#gid=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1ivpW-JmDfQvJexG0DVCQ-HWCVEaSoFL1cSjw1Ns_Qmw%2Fedit%23gid%3D0&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4wZMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=f829f4d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1ivpW-JmDfQvJexG0DVCQ-HWCVEaSoFL1cSjw1Ns_Qmw/edit#gid=0</a><br />\n主團 lhk:時代革命軍<br />\n副團 li:下格新人類團<br />\n副團2 hea:LIHKGhea打歐洲人<br />\n日文官網: <a href=\"https://bo2.ggame.jp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbo2.ggame.jp&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4wZMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=e030859b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bo2.ggame.jp</a><br />\n中文官網 : <a href=\"https://bo2.ggame.jp/hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbo2.ggame.jp%2Fhk%2F&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4wZMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=b5a3c1c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bo2.ggame.jp/hk/</a><br />\n遊戲Wiki: <a href=\"https://www65.atwiki.jp/battle-operation2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww65.atwiki.jp%2Fbattle-operation2&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4wZMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=a3142271\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www65.atwiki.jp/battle-operation2</a><br />\n新手注意<br />\n溫馨提示:咩都唔識就搵𡃁妹玩下訓練先<br />\n順手拎部200cost神器訓練吉<br />\n <br />\n <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KEKMn0X1MHk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKEKMn0X1MHk&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4wZMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=b12f60a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KEKMn0X1MHk</a><br />\n <br />\nFAQ<br />\n<br />\nQ. 點解我成日斷線<br />\nA. 為己為人, 自殺對戰請用Lan 線<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ. 今集有無EN限制?係咪好似上集兩個鐘先回1粒EN?<br />\nA. 今集廢除咗EN, 玩真人體力制, 燃燒自己嘅小宇宙啦<br />\n<br />\nQ. 有無分Server? 用港定日psn 好?<br />\nA. 今集係國際Server, 港日psn 都係一齊玩, 但之前GBON轉Server 前科, 所以用日psn應該會安全啲<br />\n<br />\nQ. 可唔可以同朋友一齊開房玩<br />\nA. Ranking 同Quick請用正方入房之後邀朋友, 自訂直接入房之後邀朋友<br />\n<br />\nQ. 點樣用支援炮擊<br />\nA. 佔點之後會見到有個數字倒數, 當倒數到0之後就可以落機call 炮擊, 威力極大如善用可以一擊逆轉戰況<br />\n<br />\nQ. 機/武/Parts 點樣升lv?<br />\nA. 用DP直接買下一lv, 如果未有得買即係未夠軍階<br />\n<br />\nQ. 點樣放炸彈<br />\nA. 1. 基礎戰先有得放<br />\n2. 去到基地搵 [ ! ]個ICON<br />\n3. 行到正確嘅位置,就會有話框叫你長按正方裝炸彈<br />\n<br />\nQ. 點樣出滾地 (緊急迴避)<br />\nA. 如果你部機有&rdquo;緊急迴避制御&ldquo; skill就可以連按兩次Boost掣使出急迴<br />\n(Default setting 即係連按X)<br />\n<br />\nQ:部機lv1用唔用到lv5武器？<br />\nA:無限場所有lv都得<br />\n限cost場要跟機lv, 高過部機過就降到你所持有嘅武器當中與機體同級或以下lv<br />\n<br />\nQ. 點樣出反格<br />\nA. 對方出格鬥時按三角撞埋去, 判定時機請自行練習<br />\n<br />\nQ. 格鬥點出二連斬三連斬<br />\nA. 機體要有&rdquo;格鬥連擊制御&ldquo; Skill, lv1可以2hit, lv2可以3hit<br />\n<br />\nQ. 點解有人可以斬完又斬好似無硬直?<br />\nA. 運用Boost Cancel 技巧就可以解除攻擊後嘅硬直(包括火箭炮, 加農炮, 格鬥, etc), 方法係攻擊後立即輕按Boost step 走<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手製SETTING建議<br />\n打之前改改手製個SETTING<br />\nDefault 用X加速搞到加速其間好難轉方向<br />\nR1轉武R2射又令人好易轉錯武<br />\n所以改成<br />\nR1射<br />\nR2轉武<br />\nL1加速<br />\nX跳<br />\n其他不變<br />\n<br />\nCredit: 浴缸裡的貓, <a href=\"http://One.For.All\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FOne.For.All&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4wZMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=319dc27f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://One.For.All</a>, 高熱火焰, 闇之大精靈<br />\n<br />\n怎麼才算好泛機隊友? #曲<br />\n1.) 開場時散開衝, 唔好係我前面阻住我衝<br />\n2.) 到主戰場企係我前面擋彈, 等我定好位先好走<br />\n3.) 我射時唔該有後眼自動遠離我射線<br />\n4.) 我比人射時唔該有NT感應BOOST過黎幫我擋彈<br />\n5.) 擋完彈之後好馬上急回彈開等我可以零秒反擊<br />\n6.) 有格機打我你地要血肉長城保護我<br />\n7.) 就算因為保護我而死, 唔該死遠D免得爆炸D光影響我, D煙唔該飄遠D唔好影響我開鏡"},{"pid":"43e79265f01c5acbe62eb0b3e0823c91838c466a","tid":2068870,"uid":243162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:05:00.000Z","msg":"抆線攻略(來源感謝抆線哥): <br />\n<br />\n其實抆線pen嘅模式唔難理解，用計分制就會明<br />\n<br />\nRank中離場（抆線）：-9<br />\nRank中連續係短時間內格隊友：-9<br />\n自訂中離場（抆線）：-7<br />\n揀機時離場：-1<br />\n打一場Rank：+1<br />\n<br />\n經驗1: 乜事都乜嘅情況下連抆兩場會pen 1, 打3-4場會解pen<br />\n<br />\n經驗2: 乜事都冇嘅情況下連抆3場變pen 2, 然後打兩場變返pen1<br />\n<br />\n以上嘅情況下計法，得出以下範圍估算<br />\n<br />\nGood: 15分-6分<br />\nCaution: 5分至0分<br />\nPenalty 1: -1至-10分<br />\nPenalty 2: -11分-18分<br />\n<br />\nQ: -18會係咩情況？<br />\nA: 已經pen 2情況下，再抆線係唔會再扣分，以及唔會禁rank（因為冇pen跌）；打所有模式都唔會有DP &amp; EXP，冇箱跌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ: pen情況下rank分數點計<br />\nA: 不論你贏幾多分都唔會加俾你，但扣分就照扣，唔會有特別懲罰<br />\n<br />\n例1: 10+7，但pen下系統會-17唔俾你加分<br />\n例2: 10-3，情況一樣，系統-7<br />\n例3: -10下贏對手+7，最終-3，系統唔會另外扣分<br />\n<br />\nQ: 有咩心得分享下？<br />\nA: 當你知道自己-18嘅情況下，可以刷首抽咁打，即係睇見果場rank就事就中離（抆線），系統唔會再有任何懲罰；重覆此舉直至刷到第一場勝利為止，至少可以令解pen嘅第一場路洗扣分先"},{"pid":"3f495e9004c6268a037756019975cbba0885fb95","tid":2068870,"uid":17459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:07:50.000Z","msg":"lm<br />\n乜料個標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">For新手 機體代號表</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1X2Hi5dLqjym5hvqX0q4NeNr_B6Eqi4Yz9Vvoapzae3s/edit?usp=sharing&amp;hl=en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1X2Hi5dLqjym5hvqX0q4NeNr_B6Eqi4Yz9Vvoapzae3s%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing%26hl%3Den&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4wZMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=721cc47f\" target=\"_blank\">http://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1X2Hi5dLqjym5hvqX0q4NeNr_B6Eqi4Yz9Vvoapzae3s/edit?usp=sharing&amp;hl=en</a>"},{"pid":"e628a7ff950bf923fee4352815148b50ca44c93c","tid":2068870,"uid":57415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:13:22.000Z","msg":"lm<br />\n點解唔忍多1個鐘先開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2f845a20f1ea796ef193693de572619dbb6376a","tid":2068870,"uid":345502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e628a7ff950bf923fee4352815148b50ca44c93c","tid":2068870,"uid":57415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:13:22.000Z","msg":"lm<br />\n點解唔忍多1個鐘先開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:14:15.000Z","msg":"俾機會GMIII 上頭版banner~"},{"pid":"ffc9b9d7aa380065e552f534fcbeea76017f6270","tid":2068870,"uid":7232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e628a7ff950bf923fee4352815148b50ca44c93c","tid":2068870,"uid":57415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:13:22.000Z","msg":"lm<br />\n點解唔忍多1個鐘先開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:14:42.000Z","msg":"記錯時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53468de0a426cd9bade1c4a35f3f506d315acdd9","tid":2068870,"uid":320881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:16:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來呢炮正是尋日軍團戰最高分果場, 亦都係我最雷果場<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />將軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />將軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />將軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n將粉團招生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p